'''STEELY-EYED MISSILE MAN''' is American Slang, circa 1960s.

A NASA Astronaut or Aerospace Engineer who makes a significant contribution or devises an ingenious solution to a tough problem.

As heard in the movie 'Apollo 13' and found in numerous biographies about NASA astronauts and ground controllers.


